---
const poster = "/images/TheReturnedPoster.jpg";
---

<section
  id="the-returned"
  class="snap-fold untimely-teaser returned-teaser"
  aria-labelledby="returned-title"
>
  <div class="untimely-teaser__atmosphere" aria-hidden="true">
    <img src={poster} alt="" />
  </div>

  <div class="untimely-teaser__inner">
    <div class="untimely-teaser__poster">
      <img
        src={poster}
        alt="The Returned"
      />
    </div>

    <article class="untimely-teaser__copy returned-teaser__copy">
      <header class="untimely-teaser__header">
        <p class="eyebrow">IN PRODUCTION</p>

        <h2 id="returned-title">
          The Returned
        </h2>
      </header>

      <div class="untimely-teaser__story returned-teaser__story">
        <p>
          Mütvia. Here rites are followed and superstitions are the law of The
          Land. Still, the dead return anyway. This is, after all, Mütvia.
        </p>

        <p class="untimely-teaser__final">
          But sometimes, even the dead don't follow the rules.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
